== Bibliography ==
* Higashi Kenshō, "The Magnates of Southern Kyushu: Saitobaru Kofun Cluster," Shinzen-sha, 2017.
* Miyazaki Prefecture Board of Education, "Reports on Geophysical Surveys of Saitobaru Kofun," 2007.

