'''Osahozuka Kofun''' ({{lang|ja|男狭穂塚古墳}}, Osahozuka Kofun) is a [[:en:Kofun|Kofun]] located in [[:en:Saito, Miyazaki|Saito City]], Miyazaki Prefecture, Japan. It is part of the [[:en:Saitobaru Kofun Cluster|Saitobaru Kofun Cluster]], specifically within the Maruyama Subcluster, and is the largest {{ill|scallop-shaped kofun|ja|帆立貝形古墳|1=Scallop Kofun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/scallop-shaped kofun|13=User:Immanuelle/Scallop Kofun|qq=}} in Japan.

While the actual honoree is unknown, the [[:en:Imperial Household Agency|Imperial Household Agency]] designates this site as the "Osahozuka {{ill|Mausoleum Reference Site|ja|陵墓参考地|1=Mausoleum Reference Site|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mausoleum Reference Site|13=User:Immanuelle/Mausoleum Reference Site|qq=}}" and identifies {{ill|Ninigi-no-Mikoto|ja|瓊瓊杵尊|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ninigi-no-Mikoto|qq=}} as the presumed honoree. It is adjacent to the {{ill|Mesahozuka Kofun|ja|女狭穂塚古墳|1=Mezasahozuka Kofun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mesahozuka Kofun|13=User:Immanuelle/Mezasahozuka Kofun|qq=}}, Historic Site1 as the "Mesahozuka {{ill|Mausoleum Reference Site|ja|陵墓参考地|1=Mausoleum Reference Site|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mausoleum Reference Site|13=User:Immanuelle/Mausoleum Reference Site|qq=}}," which is believed to honor Ninigi’s consort, {{ill|Konohanasakuya-hime|ja|木花開耶姫|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konohanasakuya-hime|qq=}}.

